            . I am an officer. In consequence of information I received from Mr. Steadman that the prisoners had obtained goods by counterfeiting orders, I and Vann apprehended them on Saturday, the 6th of January, they were identified.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18210214-36-person485">
