                  </persName>
            . I was with Mance, and took Jones in the Strand, about eight o'clock at night. We then went to a house, in Chandos-street, and there took Harrison.</p>
               <p>(order read.)</p>
               <p>Mr. Ledgworth,</p>
               <p>Sir, - I am not particular about the colour, if it is more of a purple, you may send two pieces very near the colour.</p>
